::Shredder::

Shredder looks at Lobstruck, keeping his guns aimed at him. If the other 
didn't answer soon, Shredder would open fire. He narrows his eyes, waiting 
for a responce.

Shredder nearly jumps as he hears a howl off in the distance. He growls, 
spinning around to face the direction it had come from. He looks down at his 
scanners. There were two barely detectable energy signatures in the distance 
ahead....

"Don't move. Stay right here," he tells Lobstruck, flying off toward the two 
signatures.
